_sText: This was my first bhop map when I made it in CSGO.  This is the CSS port version, and contains some different textures than the original.  Some edits have been made, but the playable area should be the same as the original, besides some teleport destinations being altered to better keep speed through resets.  There are some minor visual problems with this version, (Water, some wierd shadows) but this thing was a pain in the ass to port/compile so I'm just putting out this working version.
